嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee45c93d56282df42a48495edbb41f4b6760002","tid":300493,"uid":8352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"每次食都好似第一次食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1414503457bfebfd390c6d223d071719a084276b","tid":300493,"uid":11862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"兩包食完好似冇食過嘢咁.."},{"pid":"eb9074b336483562317a8f1cd1866dfc742f484d","tid":300493,"uid":108356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:41:47.000Z","msg":"以前好鍾意食，依家覺得個陣味好難頂，食落好想嘔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n    細個放學成日係啊波羅買營多食，個啲啊姐好多都事先整定幾個係到等人買。試過食到一次係啲麵發脹曬，啲粉溶唔曬，但我都係照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為個時窮唔係日日有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab42aab768c6676eca7ff8b1f0b3219a6c618184","tid":300493,"uid":72608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T19:08:15.000Z","msg":"以前好鐘意食, 但都係食1包<br />\n上次煮兩包黎食<br />\n陣味好難頂,好想嘔,<br />\n但食落又幾好味<br />\n不過食完覺得壽命好似短左<br />\n所以決定唔撚再食"},{"pid":"71ed725f0a38bee4c019b6ac33ebc30d357f8e3c","tid":300493,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T19:31:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聞落冇得頂<br />\n食兩三啖都仲覺得好好食<br />\n食食下開始覺得難食<br />\n食到最尾反胃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但次次半夜肚餓都要煮黎食先安樂</span></blockquote><br />\n真係唔明點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70683391bfbf059ea1a810dee3ef3d6148daaf69","tid":300493,"uid":82125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T19:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聞落冇得頂<br />\n食兩三啖都仲覺得好好食<br />\n食食下開始覺得難食<br />\n食到最尾反胃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但次次半夜肚餓都要煮黎食先安樂</span></blockquote><br />\n真係唔明點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食一包夾2下冇晒<br />\n食兩包又好快濟同難食d (唔知點解) <br />\n<br />\n其實我有諗過煮1包半 ,不過唔知另外個半包點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7f2e20e3473b473dbd9cbd027537cd9eac61af","tid":300493,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T19:40:57.000Z","msg":"食一個真係冇得頂  兩個太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbb792b68e9d273f035e265ae102213eb1f9be4","tid":300493,"uid":92857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T20:02:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聞落冇得頂<br />\n食兩三啖都仲覺得好好食<br />\n食食下開始覺得難食<br />\n食到最尾反胃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但次次半夜肚餓都要煮黎食先安樂</span></blockquote><br />\n我都覺食食下會覺得難食<br />\n但又解釋唔到點解會咁覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ea7373537fcf64bf990ae7188c29712cab5dc4","tid":300493,"uid":42636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T20:05:20.000Z","msg":"尋日食完<br />\n唔覺好食"},{"pid":"abad611545461e976e6e2ebd0abb081c85383b9a","tid":300493,"uid":68370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T20:31:34.000Z","msg":"唔落辣醬先食到最好味既撈麵。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dbd9af0868cfa4c8ccd51c62f307f447d6918b","tid":300493,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T20:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聞落冇得頂<br />\n食兩三啖都仲覺得好好食<br />\n食食下開始覺得難食<br />\n食到最尾反胃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但次次半夜肚餓都要煮黎食先安樂</span></blockquote><br />\n一包唔夠喉<br />\n但煮兩包會食到想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我煮親都係三包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed04e9a37c66d22324c8b138914af127a73eefe","tid":300493,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T20:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聞落冇得頂<br />\n食兩三啖都仲覺得好好食<br />\n食食下開始覺得難食<br />\n食到最尾反胃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但次次半夜肚餓都要煮黎食先安樂</span></blockquote><br />\n一包唔夠喉<br />\n但煮兩包會食到想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我煮親都係三包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依樣真，2包食完好似冇食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e61848a3a346f17ff7e5cd49d9ac95e5b08239","tid":300493,"uid":70092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T21:03:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聞落冇得頂<br />\n食兩三啖都仲覺得好好食<br />\n食食下開始覺得難食<br />\n食到最尾反胃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但次次半夜肚餓都要煮黎食先安樂</span></blockquote><br />\n一包唔夠喉<br />\n但煮兩包會食到想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我煮親都係三包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依樣真，2包食完好似冇食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd調味撈得唔好<br />\n沖幾多包都好一定要分開撈<br />\n一包一包咁撈再放埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f5d3b7fa13eeaccf724879d8c560ecbd42dcad","tid":300493,"uid":44044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T21:06:05.000Z","msg":"食完洗碗先難頂 勁大朕味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1496a7cc64b72c07846765de6bb90ccff33c3a","tid":300493,"uid":49153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T21:09:34.000Z","msg":"1包當下午茶<br />\n2包當lunch<br />\n3-4包當晚餐"},{"pid":"ba5c18c650b9e16ba76941304df0df37199ee484","tid":300493,"uid":99585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T21:16:11.000Z","msg":"之前有個室友係港女，應該有公主病<br />\n果日開party,飲到醉醉地，得佢無乜點飲，我地叫佢煮營多俾我地食，點知拎到岀黎變咗營多湯麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n營多湯麵其實都ok喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ecd4cb48baf325d567e246d645e2fc47769dac0","tid":300493,"uid":82997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T21:28:20.000Z","msg":"之前仲讀緊中學既時候 暑假得我一個係屋企無飯食 呀媽就買咗成箱營多返黎比我自己煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時我好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得好好味<br />\n但暑假日日係咁食 我終於明白咩叫食厭一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無野食要迫住食 食食下聞到陣味都想嘔<br />\n食完箱野 隔咗幾年先敢再食營多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db312c342f3ce6179a6395868b6a4f19ed3e4ddb","tid":300493,"uid":71502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"廢青至愛"},{"pid":"50c96a93535a2f9b50ccf79e3a8ffad667ca7be4","tid":300493,"uid":38717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T01:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢青至愛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0477f514eaebacbe0cda8990512ef5ee50ba8bf4","tid":300493,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,